ActMuseums Act
PrecisApproval of the appointment by the Minister of Canadian Heritage of DONALD A. OBONSAWIN of Whitchurch-Stouffville, Ontario, to be Vice-Chairperson of the Board of Trustees of the Canadian Museum of Nature, to hold office during pleasure for a term of four years, in the place of Glenn S. Sakaki, whose term will expire, effective May 18, 2025.
